  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>やはり時を越える聖剣ともなると
求めているのは
僕達だけじゃなかったみたいだね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Just like one could expect, it seems like we
aren't the only ones looking for the holy sword
that can pass through time itself.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>知るかよ。
オレらには譲れねぇ理由があるんだ。
相手が誰だろうとな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Heck if I care. We've got our reasons, and we
can't give this thing up. Doesn't matter who
our opponent might be.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>そうだね。
村のみんなの為にも
ここで退くわけにはいかない！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yeah. For the sake of everyone
in the village, we can't retreat!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
